<div class="navheader"><table width="100%" summary="Navigation header"><tr><th colspan="3" align="center">System Requirements</th></tr><tr><td width="20%" align="left"><a accesskey="p" href="about_purchase.php">Prev</a> </td><th width="60%" align="center">Chapter 1. About Keyman Desktop</th><td width="20%" align="right"> <a accesskey="n" href="about_history.php">Next</a></td></tr></table><hr></div><div class="section" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h2 class="title" style="clear: both" id="about_requirements">System Requirements</h2></div></div></div><h3><a name="id615782"></a>Supported Windows Operating Systems</h3><p>Keyman Desktop 8.0 fully supports 32-bit <span class="emphasis"><em>and</em></span> 64-bit versions of the following Windows operating systems:</p><div class="itemizedlist"><ul type="disc"><li><p>Windows XP (32-bit only)</p></li><li><p>Windows Server 2003</p></li><li><p>Windows Vista</p></li><li><p>Windows Server 2008</p></li><li><p>Windows 7</p></li></ul></div><div class="note" style="margin-left: 0.5in; margin-right: 0.5in;"><h3 class="title">Note</h3>Keyman Desktop works slightly differently in different versions of Windows. Older versions of Windows have more language limitations and need extra configuration. Windows Vista and later versions of Windows include added security measures and some configuration actions will require you to confirm security prompts.</div><h3><a name="id615947"></a>Resource Requirements</h3><p>Keyman Desktop 8 has minimal resource requirements. Any computer that can run Windows XP should be able to run Keyman Desktop without trouble.</p></div><div class="navfooter"><hr><table width="100%" summary="Navigation footer"><tr><td width="40%" align="left"><a accesskey="p" href="about_purchase.php">Prev</a> </td><td width="20%" align="center"><a accesskey="u" href="about.php">Up</a></td><td width="40%" align="right"> <a accesskey="n" href="about_history.php">Next</a></td></tr><tr><td width="40%" align="left" valign="top">Licensing Information </td><td width="20%" align="center"><a accesskey="h" href="index.php">Home</a></td><td width="40%" align="right" valign="top"> Version History</td></tr></table></div>
